"{\"eval_set_result_id\":\"planner_planner_eval_1778350299.7617452\",\"eval_set_result_name\":\"planner_planner_eval_1778350299.7617452\",\"eval_set_id\":\"planner_eval\",\"eval_case_results\":[{\"eval_set_file\":\"planner_eval\",\"eval_set_id\":\"planner_eval\",\"eval_id\":\"nyc\",\"final_eval_status\":2,\"eval_metric_results\":[],\"overall_eval_metric_results\":[{\"metric_name\":\"tool_trajectory_avg_score\",\"threshold\":1.0,\"score\":1.0,\"eval_status\":1},{\"metric_name\":\"response_match_score\",\"threshold\":0.7,\"score\":0.36413792,\"eval_status\":2}],\"eval_metric_result_per_invocation\":[{\"actual_invocation\":{\"invocation_id\":\"e-62ae3b12-203b-47c9-bcce-1f5ef46fdb35\",\"user_content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"Plan something for me in New York City on the weekend of May 26th 2025, and something on outdoor and food\"}],\"role\":\"user\"},\"final_response\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"Here's a creative and fun dating plan for your weekend in New York City, blending outdoor experiences with delicious food, perfectly suited for the late spring weather in May 2025. This plan focuses on exploring vibrant Brooklyn neighborhoods known for their culinary scene and stunning waterfront views.\\n\\n### Weekend Date: Brooklyn Bites & Skyline Sights\\n\\nThis plan takes you on a delightful journey through Brooklyn, combining a renowned outdoor food market, a picturesque park stroll, and dinner in a charming historic neighborhood.\\n\\n#### 1. Morning Feast at Smorgasburg Williamsburg\\n\\nKick off your Saturday with a culinary adventure at Smorgasburg, America's largest weekly open-air food market. This vibrant outdoor festival is a paradise for foodies, offering an incredible array of innovative dishes and gourmet treats from dozens of local vendors. You and your date can wander through the stalls, sampling everything from artisanal street food to unique desserts, all while soaking in the lively atmosphere and enjoying views of the Manhattan skyline. It's the perfect setting for a fun, interactive meal that caters to diverse tastes.\\n\\n*   **Name:** Smorgasburg Williamsburg (Marsha P. Johnson State Park)\\n*   **Latitude:** 40.7139\\n*   **Longitude:** -73.9664\\n*   **Description:** An iconic outdoor food market held on Saturdays, featuring over 100 local vendors offering a wide variety of delicious and unique food options. It runs from April through October.\\n\\n#### 2. Scenic Stroll through Brooklyn Bridge Park\\n\\nAfter indulging at Smorgasburg, take a leisurely journey south to Brooklyn Bridge Park, a sprawling urban oasis along the East River. You can enjoy a pleasant walk along the waterfront promenades, offering breathtaking panoramic views of the Manhattan skyline, the majestic Brooklyn Bridge, and the Statue of Liberty. The park's 85 acres feature rolling hills, beautiful gardens, and piers with various recreational areas, providing a serene escape and a picturesque backdrop for conversation and connection.\\n\\n*   **Name:** Brooklyn Bridge Park (Pier 1)\\n*   **Latitude:** 40.7024\\n*   **Longitude:** -73.9967\\n*   **Description:** An 85-acre urban park known for its stunning views of the Manhattan skyline, Brooklyn Bridge, and Statue of Liberty, with waterfront promenades, green spaces, and recreational piers.\\n\\n#### 3. Evening Delight in DUMBO\\n\\nConclude your day with a charming dinner in the DUMBO (Down Under the Manhattan Bridge Overpass) neighborhood. This historic area, nestled between the Brooklyn and Manhattan Bridges, is renowned for its cobblestone streets and converted 19th-century warehouse buildings. DUMBO offers a variety of trendy restaurants and casual eateries, many with outdoor seating options, where you can savor a delicious meal and perhaps catch a beautiful sunset over the East River. It's an ideal spot to reflect on your day and enjoy the unique, industrial-chic ambiance.\\n\\n*   **Name:** DUMBO (Down Under the Manhattan Bridge Overpass)\\n*   **Latitude:** 40.702324\\n*   **Longitude:** -73.990158\\n*   **Description:** A vibrant and historic waterfront neighborhood in Brooklyn, famous for its cobblestone streets, industrial-chic architecture, art galleries, and diverse dining options, many with scenic views.\"}],\"role\":\"model\"},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":0.0},\"expected_invocation\":{\"invocation_id\":\"e-77c5c862-68e3-45f9-90f6-3a0959aa5538\",\"user_content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"Plan something for me in New York City on the weekend of May 26th 2025, and something on outdoor and food\"}],\"role\":\"user\"},\"final_response\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":null,\"executable_code\":null,\"function_call\":null,\"function_response\":null,\"text\":\"Okay, here's a plan for a fun and delicious date in NYC, keeping your interests in mind for the weekend of May 26th, 2025:\\n\\n**Plan:** A mix of outdoor delights and foodie adventures.\\n\\n1.  **Morning Market Stroll:** (May 24, 2025)\\n\\n    *   **Activity:** Start your weekend with a visit to the **Down to Earth Morningside Park Farmers Market**. Enjoy the vibrant atmosphere, sample local produce, and pick up some delicious treats for a picnic later in the day.\\n    *   **Location:** 237-331 Manhattan Ave, New York, NY 10026, USA\\n    *   **Latitude:** 40.8053\\n    *   **Longitude:** -73.9623\\n    *   **Description:** A year-round outdoor farmers market offering fresh, local products.\\n2.  **Central Park Picnic:**\\n\\n    *   **Activity:** After the market, head to **Central Park** for a scenic picnic. **East Meadow** offers a quiet and serene atmosphere.\\n    *   **Location:** Central Park, New York, NY\\n    *   **Latitude:** 40.7829\\n    *   **Longitude:** -73.9654\\n    *   **Description:** A large green space in the heart of Manhattan, perfect for a relaxing picnic. East Meadow is dog-friendly and offers scenic views.\\n3.  **Rooftop Views & Cocktails:**\\n\\n    *   **Activity:** As the sun begins to set, make your way to a rooftop bar for drinks with a view. **Monarch Rooftop** offers amazing views of the Manhattan skyline and the Empire State Building.\\n    *   **Location:** 71 W 35th St 18th floor, New York, NY 10001\\n    *   **Latitude:** 40.7490\\n    *   **Longitude:** -73.9853\\n    *   **Description:** An extravagant penthouse lounge with floor-to-ceiling windows, offering specialty cocktails and a tapas menu. It's known for its in-house mixologist and fresh, inventive drinks.\\n\"}],\"role\":null},\"intermediate_data\":{\"tool_uses\":[],\"intermediate_responses\":[]},\"creation_timestamp\":1750478360.965003},\"eval_metric_results\":[{\"metric_name\":\"tool_trajectory_avg_score\",\"threshold\":1.0,\"score\":1.0,\"eval_status\":1},{\"metric_name\":\"response_match_score\",\"threshold\":0.7,\"score\":0.36413792,\"eval_status\":2}]}],\"session_id\":\"___eval___session___8a7b4495-cab9-4f09-81ea-e0d6adb59264\",\"session_details\":{\"id\":\"___eval___session___8a7b4495-cab9-4f09-81ea-e0d6adb59264\",\"app_name\":\"planner\",\"user_id\":\"user\",\"state\":{},\"events\":[{\"content\":{\"parts\":[{\"video_metadata\":null,\"thought\":null,\"inline_data\":null,\"file_data\":null,\"thought_signature\":null,\"code_execution_result\":n